### 敏感度指标和权重API测试

### 1. 获取所有指标信息
GET http://localhost:8000/api/indicators
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. 获取敏感度指标信息
GET http://localhost:8000/api/indicators/sensitivity
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 3. 获取指标权重信息  
GET http://localhost:8000/api/indicators/weights
Content-Type: application/json

###

